<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726406>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal and ventral view of selected Mirocastnia pyrrhopygoides canis specimens. A, B: ♀ Holotype, Junín Dept., Peru (NHMUK); C, D: ♁ Amazonas, Peru (RW); E, F: ♀ Amazonas, Peru (RW); G, H: ♁ Huánuco, Peru (RW); I, J: ♀ Huánuco, Peru (RW); K, L: ♁ Cuzco, Peru (RW); M, N: ♀ Cuzco, Peru (RW). Scale: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726406/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726408>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Size comparison of specimens of Mirocastnia pyrrhopygoides canis collected in Huánuco, Peru (RW). Scale: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726408/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726414>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Male genital capsule, dextral and sinistral view of aedeagus of the different taxa in the genus Mirocastnia. A–C: M. pyrrhopygoides canis; D, E: M. pyrrhopygoides pyrrhopygoides; F, G: M. pyrrhopygoides smalli (E–G: from Miller, 1980). Scale: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726414/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726410>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Distribution of the different taxa in the genus Mirocastnia in Central and South America." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726410/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726404>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal and ventral view of selected Mirocastnia pyrrhopygoides pyrrhopygoides specimens. A, B: ♁ Valle del Cauca, Colombia (LC) (not to scale); C, D: ♀ Risaralda, Colombia (JS); E: ♁ Lectotype, Zaruma, Ecuador (NHMUK); F: ♁ Paralectotype, Zaruma, Ecuador (NHMUK); G, H: ♀ Holotype Castnia (Schaefferia) subcoerulea, Ecuador (NHMUK); I, J: ♁ Esmeraldas, Ecuador (RW); K, L: ♀ Otongachi, Ecuador (HT). Scale: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726404/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726402>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsal and Ventral view of selected Mirocastnia pyrrhopygoides smalli specimens. A, B: ♁ Holotype, Panama (MGCL); C, D: ♀ Paratype, Panama (MGCL); E, F: ♀ Costa Rica (MNCR). Scale: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726402/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

